sources.title: FLUEGELSCHLAGEN
sources.description: With Margret Gloddek and Ingrid Lutz Der author and his partners. Multiple relationship as a way of life. The entire trilogy: 1976 Flügelschlagen (Wing flapping) Trilogie 1, 16 min 1978 Mehr als Zwei (More than two) Trilogie 2, 16:45 min 1979 Schattenkur (Cure of shadows) Trilogie 3, 15 min
